dc_title_s: Cities and Census Designated Places: Russian River Watershed, California, 1990
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile contains the boundaries of cities and other Census designated places within the Russian River Watershed region. The Federal place codes define polygons that are cities or census designated places or are unclassified as to type. The intended use for this layer is to provide GIS users with 1990 census data related to cities and Censusidesignated places within the Russian River Watershed region.
